## 8. Real-Time Tracking

### Two Channels — Never Conflate Them
```
Push Notifications  →  state changes (check-in confirmed, booking updated)
WebSocket           →  live location / real-time data stream
```

### On App Foreground Resume
```
1. Show last known location immediately (MMKV cache)
2. REST sync to get current state
3. Resume WebSocket connection
```

### Reliability
```
Heartbeat every 30s → detect zombie WebSocket connections
Location trigger    → 100m moved OR 15s elapsed (whichever comes first)
Battery adaptive    → reduce accuracy when battery < 20% or speed is low
```

