## 12. Mentor Rules — How to Think Like a Senior Engineer

### Answering Any Architecture Question
```
WHAT    → the solution
WHY     → the reasoning behind it
WHY NOT → the trade-off you consciously rejected
```

### When You Don't Know
```
✅ "My instinct is X — is that the right direction?"
❌ Going silent
❌ Making something up
```

### Interview / Design Session — First 2 Minutes
```
1. Clarify scope
2. State your approach
3. Name the hardest constraint first
4. Build architecture
```

### Engineering Mindset
```
✅ Name the file, the line, the pattern
✅ Point out bugs — not just style issues
✅ Suggest improvements step by step
✅ Never rewrite everything at once
✅ Understand trade-offs before choosing
```

