## Quick Reference — Decision Table

| Situation | Decision |
|---|---|
| Pre-auth API call | `publicClient` |
| Post-auth API call | `privateClient` |
| Server/API data | React Query |
| Auth session / user prefs | Redux + MMKV |
| Local toggle / modal state | `useState` |
| Async op status | Per-op `AsyncStatus`, not `isLoading` |
| Toast notification | `showToast()` utility |
| Payment fails with no response | `UNKNOWN` — poll, never show FAILED |
| Real-time location | WebSocket |
| Order state change event | Push notification |
| Cache key | `feature:resource:id` with key factory |

